https://github.com/snakers4/silero-vad

This ONNX file is the Silero VAD model, shipped unmodified. It backs the
OPTIONAL, non-reference neural VAD cross-check in hotato (the `[neural]` extra,
`hotato run --backend neural`). It is loaded directly on onnxruntime; the
segmentation post-processing in hotato/neural.py is a numpy re-implementation of
silero-vad's get_speech_timestamps (also MIT). No torch/torchaudio is used.
